Discussion and Conclusion¶

The purpose of the Project has been to Evaluate various categorical and Numerical Values and if they cause A positive or negative heartdisease in a sample of Patients .

The problem is a classification problem .

Analysis Of Logistic Regression

A most commonly used approach in Classification problem is Logistic Regression. A Target Variable in this case is Heart Disease , there are Independant and dependant Variable . As it can be seen the accuracy of the predicted model is higher using hyperparamtres 'newton-sg' ,penalty of l2 and max_iteration = 4000.

The accuracy is 0.9189 prcnt appoximately 92(%)

Analysis Using Decision Tree Classifier
